<body>
<div type="letter">
<pb facs="1361566" n="1"/>
<opener><lb/>Viro <abbr>Illustriss.</abbr> et <abbr>Celeber.<hi rend="sup">o</hi></abbr>
    <lb/><rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-119166895">Nicolao Bernoull<choice><orig><g ref="#j">j</g></orig><reg>i</reg></choice></rs> <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-102552517">Petrus <abbr>An.<hi rend="sup">us</hi></abbr> Michelotti</rs> <abbr>S. P. D.</abbr></opener>
<p><lb/>Tuis <rs type="letter" key="letterID">litteris</rs> mihi gratissimis hactenus non respondi
                              <lb/>quia <rs type="keyword">Transactionum philosophicarum Anglicarum</rs>
                              <lb/>transmissa Te quam maxime salutari jussi uti etiam
                              <lb/>per Illustrem Amicum nostr<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> (qui ante duos dies isthic
    <lb/>fuit, Teque videre sibi non contigit) <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-118901125">Josephum Smith</rs>.
    <lb/>Nunc protinus ad recentissimam tuam <rs type="letter" key="B_1719-04-13_991170517037005501">epistolam</rs> res<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>pondeo. Et primum quidem gratias Tibi refero maximas
                              <lb/>quod me certiorem feceris de iis qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> legisti in nuperis
    <lb/><rs type="organisation">Transactionibus Philosophicis Anglicis</rs> ad <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-11887733X">Marchionem 
        <lb/>Polen<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice></rs> non ita pridem delatis, circa articulum <rs type="biblio" key="biblio_M6Z9EVAL"><choice><orig>de</orig><reg>De</reg></choice> motu
            <lb/>aquarum fluentium</rs> Authore <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-119507978">Jacobo Jurino <abbr>M. D.</abbr></rs> Scribo
    <lb/>hanc quam Tibi commendo <rs type="letter" key="letterID">epistolam</rs><!-- ToDo: Dieser Brief von Michelotti an Poleni ist vermutlich nicht erhalten. (Eventuell in der Biblioteca Marciana vorhanden). --> ad <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-11887733X">Polenum</rs> <del>ipsum</del>
<lb/>rogatum ut volumen istud commodet per aliquod
                              <lb/>tempus. Quum <subst><del><gap/></del><add>p</add></subst>erlego refutare conabor iis qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>
    <lb/>a Te accepi principiis, omniaque, et Tibi et <abbr>Illustriss.<hi rend="sup">o</hi></abbr>
    <lb/><rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-118509969">Patruo</rs> communicabo, quem salutatum a Te meo
    <lb/>nomine quamprimum fieri poterit per <rs type="letter" key="letterID">literas</rs> cupio:
                              <lb/>quibus eidem nunciare poteris me propediem
    <lb/><add>sibi </add>transmissur<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> meam <rs type="biblio" key="biblio_M3G2JA79">dissertationem</rs>, cui fere finem
                              <lb/>feci. Interim recorderis velim appropinquare vaca<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>tionum magnorum tempus quo Te huc venire mo<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>raturum domi me<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> etiam atque etiam rogo ut possim
                              <lb/>et Tibi inservire, et fructus insignes in rebus mathe<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>maticis, mechanicisque per mutua colloquia conquire<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>re. <date>Hodie</date> <abbr>Illustr.</abbr> <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-118901125">Joseph Smith</rs> hinc discedens huc
    <lb/>proficiscitur una cum <abbr>Ill.</abbr> sua <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-1228890153">uxore</rs>. Te igitur hortor
                              <lb/>ut cras ad illum eas salutatum. Habitabit credo in
    <lb/>Palatio, quod vulgo <rs type="place" key="GeoNamesID">Ca Cavalli</rs><!-- San Polo 1948 --> isthic appellant. Si <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-11887733X">Polenus</rs>
                              <pb facs="1361568" n="2"/>
    <lb/>commemoratum volumen <rs type="keyword"><abbr>Transact.</abbr> Anglicar<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice></rs> mihi com<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>modare non recusabit, ipse <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-118901125">Smith</rs> illud ad me defer<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>re rogatus dignabitur.</p> <closer><salute>Vale Vir Amicissimi mihique
    <lb/>uti assoles favere perge.</salute> <dateline>Dabam <rs type="place" key="place_VER-repven">Venetiis</rs> <choice><abbr>a. d.</abbr><expan>a dato</expan></choice> <date when="1719-04-16">16 
        <lb/>Aprilis 1719.</date></dateline></closer>
    <note hand="pers_DE-588-119166895"><foreign xml:lang="ger"><abbr>Empf.</abbr> den <date when="1719-04-18">18<hi rend="sup">ten</hi></date></foreign></note>
</div>
